### 安全检查脚本

```bash
#!/bin/bash
# scripts/security-check.sh

echo "🔒 Running security checks..."

# 1. 检查 .env 文件是否在版本控制中
if git ls-files | grep -q "^\.env$"; then
  echo "❌ ERROR: .env file is tracked by git!"
  exit 1
fi

# 2. 检查敏感文件权限
chmod 600 .env 2>/dev/null || echo "⚠️  .env not found"

# 3. 运行依赖漏洞扫描
npm audit --audit-level=high

# 4. 检查 TypeScript 编译
npm run build

# 5. 运行测试
npm test

# 6. 检查代码质量
npm run lint 2>/dev/null || echo "⚠️  Lint script not found"

echo "✅ Security checks completed!"
```

